RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT CUSTOMER_NO, ENTITY_ID FROM OLtb_contract_entity WHERE CONTRACT_REF_NO = ? AND PRIMARY_ENTITY = 'Y'

SELECT 'FPML' MEDIA FROM (SELECT COUNT(1) CNT FROM OLTB_CONTRACT_ENTITY ENT, OLTMS_CUSTOMER_ENTITY_DETAILS DTL1 WHERE ENT.CONTRACT_REF_NO = ? AND ENT.CUSTOMER_NO = DTL1.CUSTOMER_NO AND ENT.EVENT_SEQ_NO = (SELECT MAX(EVENT_SEQ_NO) FROM OLTB_CONTRACT_ENTITY ENT1 WHERE ENT1.CONTRACT_REF_NO = ENT.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND ENT1.CUSTOMER_NO = ENT.CUSTOMER_NO) AND ENT.ENTITY_ID = DTL1.ENTITY AND NVL(DTL1.SEND_FPML,'N') <> 'Y') WHERE CNT = 0 UNION SELECT 'EMAIL' FROM (SELECT COUNT(1) CNT FROM OLTB_CONTRACT_ENTITY ENT, OLTMS_CUSTOMER_ENTITY_DETAILS DTL1 WHERE ENT.CONTRACT_REF_NO = ? AND ENT.EVENT_SEQ_NO = (SELECT MAX(EVENT_SEQ_NO) FROM OLTB_CONTRACT_ENTITY ENT1 WHERE ENT1.CONTRACT_REF_NO = ENT.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND ENT1.CUSTOMER_NO = ENT.CUSTOMER_NO) AND ENT.CUSTOMER_NO = DTL1.CUSTOMER_NO AND ENT.ENTITY_ID = DTL1.ENTITY AND NVL(DTL1.SEND_BYEMAIL,'N') <> 'Y') WHERE CNT = 0 UNION SELECT 'FAX' FROM (SELECT COUNT(1) CNT FROM OLTB_CONTRACT_ENTITY ENT, OLTMS_CUSTOMER_ENTITY_DETAILS DTL1 WHERE ENT.CONTRACT_REF_NO = ? AND ENT.EVENT_SEQ_NO = (SELECT MAX(EVENT_SEQ_NO) FROM OLTB_CONTRACT_ENTITY ENT1 WHERE ENT1.CONTRACT_REF_NO = ENT.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND ENT1.CUSTOMER_NO = ENT.CUSTOMER_NO) AND ENT.CUSTOMER_NO = DTL1.CUSTOMER_NO AND ENT.ENTITY_ID = DTL1.ENTITY AND NVL(DTL1.SEND_BYFAX,'N') <> 'Y') WHERE CNT = 0
